# Code Organization

## Directory Structure
- [src/app](mdc:src/app) - Next.js app router pages and layouts
- [src/components](mdc:src/components) - Reusable React components
- [src/hooks](mdc:src/hooks) - Custom React hooks
- [src/context](mdc:src/context) - React context providers
- [src/services](mdc:src/services) - API services for data fetching
- [src/lib](mdc:src/lib) - Utility functions and common libraries
- [src/types](mdc:src/types) - TypeScript type definitions
- [src/data](mdc:src/data) - Mock data and constants

## Component Structure
- UI components are built using Shadcn UI
- Feature components are organized by domain (expenses, groups, payments)
- Layout components handle page structure
